<div id="pf5a" class="pf w6 h12" data-page-no="5a"><div class="pc pc5a w6 h12"><img class="bi x0 y0 w7 h13" alt="" src="bg5a.png"/><div class="t m2a7 x12 h2a yeb ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 11 </div><div class="t m16 x70 h2a y53f ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t m349 x51 h2a y253 ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">March 10-16 </div><div class="t m68a x8b h1e yb92 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Do a Bible </div><div class="t m6a9 xb0 h1e y31 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Word Study </div><div class="t m6aa x65 h1e y407 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;\\N </div><div class="t m2f2 x12 h24 yb76 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath Afternoon </div><div class="t m5c6 x12 h25 yb93 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READ FOR THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Lev. 19:11-16; Psalm 12; </div><div class="t m59b x6 h25 yace ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prov. 30:5, 6; Matt. 5:13-16; 20:26; Luke 10:29-42; Rom. 6:15-</div><div class="t m211 x6 h25 y5c9 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">23. </div><div class="t m473 x2f h25 yb94 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: &quot;And the King will answer and say to </div><div class="t m3f8 x2f h25 yb95 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them, &apos;Assuredly, I say to you, inasmuch as you did it to one of </div><div class="t m6ab x2f h25 yafc ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the least of these My brethren, you did it to Me&apos; &quot; (Matthew </div><div class="t m605 x2f h25 yb96 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25:40, NKJV). </div><div class="t me7 x5 h25 yafd ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHT: </div><div class="t m541 xc6 h26 yafd ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This lesson seeks to demonstrate the effec-</div><div class="t m440 x6 h26 y26c ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tiveness of Bible word studies. The word we will study is </div><div class="t m147 x5c h26 y5cc ff5 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">service. </div><div class="t me8 x6 h26 yb97 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One way the gospel becomes real to others is by acts of kindness, </div><div class="t m6ac x6 h26 y5b9 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">compassion, and unselfishness performed by those who value the gift </div><div class="t m15d x6 h26 yb98 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of salvation and fulfill their responsibility to the world. </div><div class="t m279 x5 h25 y5d0 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WHAT IS SERVICE ALL ABOUT? </div><div class="t m1d9 x9e h26 yb99 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Service can take many </div><div class="t m2ee x6 h26 y5d1 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forms. It may be practical service to those in need, service of various </div><div class="t mc4 x6 h26 y5d2 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kinds for the church, witnessing to the centrality of Jesus in our lives, </div><div class="t m42d x12 h26 y5d3 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">or teaching others God&apos;s special message for the last days. Whatever </div><div class="t m6ad x6 h26 y5d4 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it is, we place ourselves at God&apos;s disposal to be His instruments. </div><div class="t m12c x6 h26 y5d5 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Service is part of our sanctification; we are set apart to be used by </div><div class="t m2ce x12 h26 y5d6 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. Service can bring peace to families, communities, churches, </div><div class="t m6ae x6 h26 y10d ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to our own lives through presenting Jesus as the answer to human </div><div class="t m658 x6 h26 y5d8 ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need. Service implements mercy and justice in our relationships with </div><div class="t m68d x12 h26 yb9a ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others. </div><div class="t m106 x6 h26 y53e ff4 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">88 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
